🔐 How It Works

Type 1234 in Serial Monitor → Door unlocks ✅

Wrong password → stays locked ❌

Button pressed → bell sound 🔔

Potentiometer → changes buzzer tone 🎛️

LEDs show lock status 🔴🟢



